snippet.title: Super Mario RPG: The Starlite Worlds Teaser
snippet.description:
GET DEMO HERE:
http://udivision.blogspot.com/2010/06/download-page-super-mario-rpg-starlite.html

Other Links:
http://icugigasoft.freeforums.org
http://udivision.blogspot.com/
http://cdivisionworks.blogspot.com/

What you are about to see are clips from the upcoming  C-Division and U Division collaborative project, codenamed "Mario XP." This game is still in the early alpha stages of development, and the video you are about to see represents only four days of work on the project. It's still very rough, and elements you see here may not end up in the final version of the project.
